sub_title: Marketing & Communications Director High Tech Campus Eindhoven, Co-Founder Female Tech Heroes
summary:
Hi! I'm an experienced marketeer, communicator and manager, proudly working at the smartest km² in the Netherlands: High Tech Campus Eindhoven. I have a proven track record in Marketing Strategy, Digital Marketing, Marketing Automation, Inbound Marketing, International Business Development, PR, Marketing Communications, Social Media and Event Management. But most important, I like to connect and work with enthusiastic and interesting people on different projects to expand my network and to make our beautiful Brainport region a great place to live and work!

Furthermore I'm the Co-Founder of Female Tech Heroes, a new initiative dedicated to women working in technology. We want to inspire women in tech, but also women who are curious about tech. Founders Ingelou Stol & Hilde de Vocht: 'At present, the percentage of women working in tech worldwide is still relatively low. 'We work in an environment heavily dominated by men, and we need more women. Diversity is the key to success. 'Research shows that diverse teams perform better. Individuals from different genders, races, backgrounds and experiences bring different perspectives that can lead to innovative solutions. Having key women in senior leadership roles will positively encourage other females to join an organisation that is supportive of advancing women’s careers, thus increasing overall company growth and productivity.'

✦About High Tech Campus Eindhoven:
High Tech Campus Eindhoven is the smartest km² in The Netherlands with more than 280 companies and institutes, and some 12,000 researchers, developers and entrepreneurs working on developing future technologies and products. The Campus helps companies accelerate their innovation by offering easy access to high tech facilities and international networks. www.hightechcampus.com
